What I really meant to say was that the line about guilds wanting a CoF or RBB was a minor point and shouldn't be taken as the cornerstone of my argument.  I got it wrong, and please excuse me for that.  I really wasn't trying to insinuate that the larger guilds would &quot;oppress the weak&quot; or anything as paranoid or delusional as that.  The only haste number I really know a lot about is 65% (what Burnout IV gives my pet) and I'll figure out Muzzle of Mardu sometime soon.<br>
